        "title": "feat(calendar): add 'changed' command to list recently modified events",
        "body": "Adds `gog calendar changed` (aliases: recent, modified) which surfaces the N events most recently created or modified, sorted by last-modification time descending. Uses Events.List with UpdatedMin and omits SingleEvents so that recurring series appear as a single master entry rather than exploding into per-instance results. Supports --since (duration/date/RFC3339, default 30d), --max, --all, --cal, --calendars, --show-deleted, --weekday, --location, and --fail-empty flags.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1803\" height=\"381\" alt=\"Screenshot-2026-06-23_16:17:31\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/562eb957-ba0b-42ea-85ea-e8834300418f\" />\r\n",
